{"TopicId":157535,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"SAS: Hold Horizon","CreatedByName":"MajorNr01","CreatedById":43823,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-09T21:14:58Z","PageNum":4,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"razark","CreatedById":32993,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-27T01:03:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223035958\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157535\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221493254609\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022126909\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SchweinAero\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, SchweinAero said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAre there any people who support not supporting this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhile I support this, I support not supporting this, because everyone is entitled to their own opinion, however wrong they may be.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pthigrivi","CreatedById":105624,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-27T02:11:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t support half of this half as well as I should like, and I support less than half of this half as well as it deserves.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"qzgy","CreatedById":160994,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-27T02:37:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSupport not I do not.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003EAnybody else notice how weird the word \u0022support\u0022 is?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-04-27T02:37:57Z\u0022 title=\u002204/27/2017 02:37  AM\u0022 data-short=\